name: Giant Clam Shell
category: Decorative
footprint: 2x2
facing: no
shadow: yes
blocks_light: no
height: 1.0
placement: center
room_types: elemental-water-node, aquatic-shrine, sunken-temple, merfolk-grotto, coral-reef
typical_count: single
clusters_with: pearl-cluster, shell-scatter, anemone-glow, marid-pavilion
notes: Enormous open clam with pearl inside; place as single centerpiece or small focal point
